parameters:
Clea: It's an empty shell. There are traces of it being used
as a warehouse, but...
Celis of the Swift Wind: Clea... it's dangerous.

Member of the Loparo Plunder Gang: Hehehe, Psema-san was
right. If we leave a note, annoying people will gather on
their own!

Loparo Plunder Gang Member: We won't leave a single one of
those imperial dogs alive.
Celis of the Swift Wind: Clea... are you okay?
Clea: Yes, thank you very much.

Celis of the Swift Wind: As an examiner today, don't let
your guard down at the entrance. It will be deducted points.

Celis of the Swift Wind: Defeat these guys to make up for it
and show them.

Roparo Raiders Member: Hmph, nothing special! I'll kill
everyone, including the women in the back!
Celis, the Gale: Clea, take a rest.

Celis, the Gale: Clea has good technique, but in battles
with too many unnecessary movements, if she lets her body
become one with the wind... no one can touch her.
Celis, the Gale: Well then, let's hear what you have to say.
Celis of the Gale Where is the dragon's tear that was here?

Member of the Loparo Plunder Gang: It's scattered all over
the empire! Everything was too late, you dogs of the empire.

Celis of the Gale: I'll ask one more time, where is the
dragon's tear that was here?

Loparo Plunder Gang Member: That's why, it's scattered all
over the empire--

Loparo Plunder Gang Member: ...Why did you, you, draw your
sword on my hair, hey!

Celis of the Gale: Next, your ears will be cut off. Where is
the dragon's tear that was here?
